OL,3,CHospitality staff could have hours cut
OL,4,Cto combat quiet winter months
OL,6,FWorkers at three Channel Island hotels
OL,7,Fcould have their hours, and as a
OL,8,Fresult their pay, cut to combat the
OL,9,Fquiet winter period, according to a
OL,10,Fletter sent to staff and seen by ITV
OL,11,FNews.
OL,13,FHand Picked Hotels - which runs sites
OL,14,Flike L'Horizon in Jersey and St Pierre
OL,15,FPark in Guernsey - is reducing some
OL,16,Femployee's hours by 12.5%, due to a
OL,17,Flack of bookings this time of year.
OL,19,FThe decision, the letter says, has
OL,20,Fbeen taken due to a "diminution in
OL,21,Fwork" over the period.
