OL,3,CHospitality staff could have hours cut
OL,4,Cto combat quiet winter months
OL,6,FHand Picked Hotel Group has 21 luxury
OL,7,Fproperties in the UK and the Channel
OL,8,FIslands.
OL,10,FStaff at Grand Jersey Hotel & Spa and
OL,11,FFermain Valley Hotel in Guernsey are
OL,12,Famong those affected.
OL,14,FOne member of staff, speaking
OL,15,Fanonymously, said some staff are
OL,16,Fthinking of leaving due to the
OL,17,Fdecision.
OL,19,F"We have just had to work really hard
OL,20,Fand endless hours over Christmas and
OL,21,Fthey do this" the employee said.
