OL,3,CHospitality staff could have hours cut
OL,4,Cto combat quiet winter months
OL,6,FThe period between Christmas and the
OL,7,FSpring is particularly challenging for
OL,8,Fthe hospitality industry. However,
OL,9,Fhoteliers and travel experts have told
OL,10,FITV News that this year is proving
OL,11,Fespecially challenging.
OL,13,FRobert McKenzie is a Channel Islands
OL,14,Ftravel agent and blames the cost of
OL,15,Fliving crisis in the UK for hitting
OL,16,Fwinter tourism.
