OL,3,CHospitality staff could have hours cut
OL,4,Cto combat quiet winter months
OL,6,FHe says: "People's disposable income,
OL,7,Fdiscretionary income is under
OL,8,Fpressure. So I think people are
OL,9,Flooking to cut back on maybe short
OL,10,Fbreaks and holidays in the off-season
OL,11,Fand focus on still being able to take
OL,12,Fa holiday in the summer."
OL,14,FA Hand Picked Hotels spokesperson said:
