OL,3,CHospitality staff could have hours cut
OL,4,Cto combat quiet winter months
OL,6,F"Hand Picked Hotels, facing
OL,7,Fchallenging market headwinds and
OL,8,Freduced guest demand, has alongside
OL,9,Fmany other hotel and hospitality
OL,10,Fbusinesses in the UK, made the tough
OL,11,Fdecision to reduce the number of
OL,12,Fpayroll hours in the short-term, by up
OL,13,Fto 12.5% in total. This is not a
OL,14,Fdecision we have taken lightly.
OL,16,F"The hospitality industry in the UK
OL,17,Fwas devastated by Covid and in most
OL,18,Fcases had only just got back to
OL,19,Fbreaking even in late 2022.
